      "correctAnswer": "unset VAR",
      "explanation": "The unset command removes the specified variable or function from the shell.",
      "difficulty": "easy"
    },
    {
      "id": "mcq-6",
      "question": "What does the $HOME environment variable represent?",
      "options": [
